# Summary

The Friends Like These application integrates multiple cloud services to provide a responsive, real-time event management platform.

Firebase provides real-time data synchronisation, Google Forms simplifies participant registration, Google Sheets stores registration data, and QR code integration streamlines participant access.

The modular API architecture allows the application to evolve into a full enterprise solution with a dedicated backend and RESTful API while maintaining a clear separation between presentation, business logic, and external services.
